node.text: Thank you so much @therealmaryjblige for this amazing box. You are undeniably talented and amazing at what you do. Very honored to receive one of these. My mom is already trying to fight me behind this record 😂. Thank you to @amazonprimevideo as well. If you haven’t already checked out @therealmaryjblige documentary. You can on @amazonprimevideo

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wuzzam Supa on July 09, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and indoor.

node.text: Just wanted you to know bro…I made it out the Jungle. Haven’t been to jail in over 5 years, I don’t miss no rent payments, my car don’t run hot anymore. I don’t wait on tables anymore. Even tho that was my favorite job. You knew that. That’s why you’ll come and sit in my section. Just so you could keep me updated. I moved to where I don’t hear gunshots no more. I have a daughter brother. She’s amazing. I’m making sure my children doesn’t witness what we did. I know you been seeing how god has been blessing me. I hope you are proud of me. I love you Vish. Love you so much. Goodnight big baby #LongLiveVish
